node.text:
I had an incredible time on planet Burning Man & took my time editing & reliving the experience. This year was one of my favorites... I got to witnessing Burning Man through a new lens🙌🏽 Tag 3 friends you would go to Burning Man with. 
tawnyjanae 
Music @brock.berrigan

Drone Shots  @jacob
Timelapse  @vlvart
Drone Shots - Vaeilie -

#burningman #burningman2019 #burningmanstyle

node.text: Few days ago I spoke on my anxiety and mental health. I want to thank you all that have reached out. I was a little nervous to get that vulnerable with everyone that follows me. But what I realized is we should be doing this. Especially people with large following. Large influencers just put out beautiful lives, flexing with Material things, etc. Also I’ve done this. I think it’s good sometimes to be relatable we need to let people know that they’re not alone and help educate. So that being said whenever I need to move my anxiety I like to work out at the gym. what some of yours? 📸 @juditmoreno22
